  ],
  "remarks": "Alla Barkhatnova has been the so-called “Minister of Labour and Social Policy” of Kherson Region since 25 October 2023. She is responsible for overseeing the integration of those areas of Kherson not under Ukrainian control into the Russian Federation, by implementing Russia’s social policy measures and initiatives. She has also been involved with the illegal deportation and re-education of Ukrainian children, including their deportation into Russia.",
